{"tid":1728734,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［NS]Pokemon劍盾修改討論區 1","createTime":"2019-11-17T03:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T15:45:03.000Z","uid":74266,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6a879bb0332e14f6aa3682660d7936410ba61c5","tid":1728734,"uid":74266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/04/yR9KpW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F04%2FyR9KpW.png&h=61d6ecb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此POST並非小圈子<br />\n歡迎討論修改<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請支持官方授權<br />\n<br />\n香港Pok&eacute;mon比賽</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://playpokemonhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaypokemonhk.com%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=988f2c23\" target=\"_blank\">http://playpokemonhk.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PlayPokemonHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPlayPokemonHK%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=021b8b2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PlayPokemonHK/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Q&amp;A</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 我買日版遊戲會唔會有中文？</strong><br />\n買咩版都有齊九國語言 記住冇得中途改 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 點解刷極都係女比卡超/伊貝既？我想要仔</strong><br />\n性別係開game一刻就鎖定左 要刷就要由頭玩過 <br />\n性格就可以係草前面save再刷<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 咁點樣刪save？</strong><br />\n入Switch setting搞<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 比卡超、伊貝同夢夢咩性格好？</strong><br />\n比卡超：只玩特攻-timid 雙刀-naive/hasty<br />\n伊貝： 暫時推介adamant (玩專用技可考慮Modest, 只對人戰亦可考慮加防/特防性格)<br />\n夢夢： 好多性格都得 但做攻手唔夠超夢夢/富迪爭 刷Bold當盾都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n性格表google下就會有 *如果過關爆機就棄game的話其實冇必要刷*<br />\n<br />\n<strong>5. 咩係連鎖？</strong><br />\n淨係撞同一隻，狂捉<br />\n中間唔可以遇其他寵<br />\n如果遇左其他寵走佬就得<br />\n即係連續30場捉同一隻全部捉晒<br />\n30連後有機會出6V 同提高出色違機率<br />\n<br />\n<strong>6. 邊度Check 6V? 咩係6V？</strong><br />\nCheck V 地點: 11號道路通道上層博士<br />\nV係指單項個體值最高(31), 6V就係6項個體值皆最高<br />\n留意6V唔代表最完美 特攻型精靈應該刷5V 0攻<br />\n<br />\n<strong>7. 粒波點熄聲？</strong><br />\n中間粒制同頂制 兩個制一齊禁<br />\n入左精靈之後，長按粒的，之後變左精靈隻色再即刻按頂果粒制，會即刻震，就ok<br />\n可能要拎左夢夢先熄得聲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>8. 皮卡丘伊布胡地快龍拉普拉斯超夢我想知呢...</strong><br />\n冇人識你依堆咩黎 想討論唔該用返港式譯名<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>參考網站(USUM資訊)</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n培育入門<span style=\"color: red;\">(新手必睇)</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tut1.hkgpkm.pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftut1.hkgpkm.pw&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=8f8010ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://tut1.hkgpkm.pw</a><br />\n<br />\n傷害計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pokemon-trainer.net/sm/dmcs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokemon-trainer.net%2Fsm%2Fdmcs%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=f0325c43\" target=\"_blank\">https://pokemon-trainer.net/sm/dmcs/</a> (日)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pokemonshowdown.com/damagecalc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokemonshowdown.com%2Fdamagecalc%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=1f7990ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://pokemonshowdown.com/damagecalc/</a> (英)<br />\n<br />\n個體計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.serebii.net/games/iv-calcsm.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.serebii.net%2Fgames%2Fiv-calcsm.shtml&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=564c29c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.serebii.net/games/iv-calcsm.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n最大耐久指數計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://pkc.client.jp/w/defmax.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpkc.client.jp%2Fw%2Fdefmax.html&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=177371e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://pkc.client.jp/w/defmax.html</a> (日)<br />\n<br />\n圖鑑/資料網站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://serebii.net/pokedex-sm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fserebii.net%2Fpokedex-sm%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=09964bfb\" target=\"_blank\">http://serebii.net/pokedex-sm/</a> (英)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bokevon.web.fc2.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbokevon.web.fc2.com%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=708b32ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://bokevon.web.fc2.com/</a> (英日中)"},{"pid":"628e7c5f895b3fcc801e03da1d86dcac688a1a1e","tid":1728734,"uid":74266,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"PKHeX<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.3h3.com/patch/157076.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.3h3.com%2Fpatch%2F157076.html&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=88fe7412\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.3h3.com/patch/157076.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔改機 用唔用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619a9e9b571ae882c944c246e9e2c13989c1d65a","tid":1728734,"uid":74266,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:03:23.000Z","msg":"要寵不求人<br />\n自改6V,配招<br />\n輕鬆砌隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n節省大量時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809cc5011b50fe4360fa8d46826f7016f082d5cf","tid":1728734,"uid":74266,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:09:06.000Z","msg":"乞黎乞去好麻煩<br />\n直接改好過<br />\n有冇巴打用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ba766885c27ca